content.query:
SELECT [ecEventGkey]
,[cheKind]
,[CHE_Name]
,[CHE_ID]
,[eventTypeDescription]
,[unit]
,[pow]
,[pool]
,[workQueue]
,[travelDistance]
,[moveKind]
,[startDistance]
,[operator_name]
,[EcEventTime]
,[Year]
,[Month]
,[Week]
 FROM [dbo].[ecevents]
 Where Year=2025 AND Month=10 AND Week = 42 AND DAY(EcEventTime) >=11 and DAY(EcEventTime) <=14
 ORDER by [EcEventTime] ASC, [ecEventGkey] ASC;
